nodes.text: A male urchin resided on the planet Corellia during the Imperial Era. While the rogue archaeologist Doctor Chelli Aphra waited outside the residence of the smuggler Sana Starros overnight, the urchin attempted to rob her of her belt. Aphra stopped the urchin, bribing him to bring her sweet rolls from the nearby Eim'ir's Bakery, which she later used as a bribe for Starros.
